<h2>Monitoring the UV/Ion Shield Health</h2>
<p>
In the tables below the exposure times have been corrected for dead-time after fixing the DTCOR values for the double-counting of events (done automatically in pipeline processing in DS 7.3 - July 2004).
</p>

<h3>HRC-I</h3>
<h4> On-axis</h4>
<p>
Background-subtracted source rates:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Source region centered at the RA and Dec of AR Lac</li>
    <li>Source region 4 arcsec radius</li>
    <li>Annular background region, concentric with source region, inner radius 8 arcsec outer radius 12 arcsec </li>
</ul>

